Package main.java.breakoutgame.GameHelpers

Class GameObject

java.lang.Object
main.java.breakoutgame.GameHelpers.GameObject
All Implemented Interfaces:
main.java.breakoutgame.Utils.Loggable
public abstract class GameObject
extends java.lang.Object
implements main.java.breakoutgame.Utils.Loggable
Basic abstract class for motionless GameObject. Implements Loggable interface and can be subject to property change listener (observable).
See Also:
DynamicGameObject, Loggable, PropertyChangeSupport
